{"tid":404513,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[耳機] UM1一邊冇聲維修問題","createTime":"2017-09-18T07:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T07:35:35.000Z","uid":72687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"372b17b079f2ebf1e56e8f1c84e5616e417f9901","tid":404513,"uid":72687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"買左隻R4之後, 兩年都冇用過隻UM1 <br />\n最近拎出黎試下, 點知一邊冇聲 <br />\n打去恆源問, 檢查都收380蚊 <br />\n如要換單元, 要再加錢 <br />\n買隻新既都係700蚊 <br />\n依D入門耳機, 係唔係冇人會選擇整, <br />\n大家都選擇買個隻新既? <br />\n會唔會有地方平D, <br />\n畢竟用左七八年有感情 <br />\n唔該曬"},{"pid":"ca9c63f0df40f131042b4c815fc2e0df49b70dd0","tid":404513,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"轉beyerdynamic啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afe674297cd53c56e38f498450373f235807e2d","tid":404513,"uid":146893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"可以試下搵小寶<br />\nGOOGLE SEARCH KEY WORD 「小寶」「耳機」就會搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d41585f2f048459d4c5163a006af4f68f8b18d5","tid":404513,"uid":146893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"「有不少客人會打電話或用 WhatsApp 向他查詢，耳機單邊冇聲，維修費用多少。「其實我真係答唔到，因為引致單邊冇聲的原因可以有 6 至 8 個，價錢可以好平，亦可以好貴，平則壞咗插頭，貴則燒咗嗰單元。」所以他不能在電話報到一個準確的價錢，以上來店舖即時報價為準，再者，檢查耳機是免費的，向客人解釋清楚接受報價才進行維修。萬一維修不成功的話，絕不會收取分毫。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource from:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.spill.hk/headphones/Hercules-Fix-n-Treasures-Workshop-Headphone-Feature/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spill.hk%2Fheadphones%2FHercules-Fix-n-Treasures-Workshop-Headphone-Feature%2F&d=qjisSiChuLuju8hXnyZbiJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=77abffef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.spill.hk/headphones/Hercules-Fix-n-Treasures-Workshop-Headphone-Feature/</a>"},{"pid":"bfe60cb7b6050ff94c59f227abce1b293604e933","tid":404513,"uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"搵小寶工作室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}